{"word":"Jonathan","slug":"jonathan","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Jonathan</b> - <b>(a)</b> A Levite, son of Gershom<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=7&chapter=17&verse=7'>Jdg 17:7</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=7&chapter=18&verse=30'>Jdg 18:30</a><p/><b>(b)</b> Son of Saul<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=14&verse=1'>1Sa 14:1</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=14&verse=27'>1Sa 14:27</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=14&verse=43'>1Sa 14:43</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=14&verse=49'>1Sa 14:49</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=18&verse=1'>1Sa 18:1</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=19&verse=2'>1Sa 19:2</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=20&verse=4'>1Sa 20:4</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=31&verse=2'>1Sa 31:2</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=1&verse=17'>2Sa 1:17</a><p/>--\"The Generous Friend\", Characteristics of<p/>--Heroic faith<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=14&verse=6'>1Sa 14:6</a><p/>--Undaunted courage<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=14&verse=7'>1Sa 14:7-13</a><p/>--Self-sacrificing friendship<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=18&verse=4'>1Sa 18:4</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=19&verse=2'>1Sa 19:2</a><p/><b>(c)</b> Son of Abiathar<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=15&verse=27'>2Sa 15:27</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=17&verse=17'>2Sa 17:17</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=1&verse=42'>1Ki 1:42</a><p/><b>(d)</b> One of David's Warriors<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=21&verse=21'>2Sa 21:21</a>; <a href='https://w